OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny lingering rain in the east
OL,6,Fquickly clearing, leaving a blustery
OL,7,Fday with a mix of sunshine and
OL,8,Fshowers. The showers will be heavy and
OL,9,Fpossibly thundery, before easing
OL,10,Flater. Warm in the sunny spells, but
OL,11,Fbreezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers continuing through
OL,14,Fthe evening, but becoming lighter and
OL,15,Fgradually easing overnight. Staying
OL,16,Fbreezy, rather cloudy and mild across
OL,17,Fthe country.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
