OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FLargely cloudy at first on
OL,6,FWednesday, but some brighter spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping at times. A few spots of
OL,8,Frain possible where the cloud thickens.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FTurning drier, brighter and warmer
OL,12,Fthrough Thursday. Very warm on Friday
OL,13,Fand Saturday, although some thundery
OL,14,Fshowers are possible at times.
